      "content": "okay i hear you. if sudafed is a big no, what about antibiotics? my sinus pressure is getting so bad i'm worried it might turn into something worse like an ear infection. would something like ciprofloxacin be okay to take for a few days just to clear the infection? i really just want to get this cleared up quickly so i can function again.",
